## Summary
Amplitude Data provides governance tools for defining, tracking, verifying, and improving data quality, including planning features to create specifications directly in Amplitude, the Ampli developer toolkit for type-safe tracking, and data management capabilities for metadata enrichment, data cleanup, custom event creation, and real-time monitoring through observability.

